                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10272" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2595</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">268 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">亨通光电：通信网络全产业链纵向整合的创新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hengtong - Communication network industrial chain in-depth integration and innovation road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吴东，林心怡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏亨通光电股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全产业链；通信网络；二次创新；制造服务化；2025百优案例；重点项目4-1</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The entire industrial chain, communication network, secondary innovation, manufacturing service-oriented</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为长期深耕通信光纤光缆细分领域的单项冠军企业，亨通光电既在专业化竞争中形成了领先优势，又面临利基市场容量与能力刚性约束的双重挑战。亨通光电通过持续创新，成功实现了通信网络全产业链的整合。第一阶段，公司从电缆起家，凭借“借鸡生蛋、借梯登高、借船出海 ”的三借策略快速成为电缆领域的领导者。第二阶段，为了打破对产业链上游国外光纤原材料的依赖，亨通自主研发光纤和光纤预制棒技术，成功掌握了关键核心技术，成为全球光纤通信领域的领导者。第三阶段，亨通光电通过布局产业链下游市场，推出光纤到户解决方案，并整合服务资源，转型为“产品+服务”总包模式，进入智慧城市和海洋通信等新兴领域。其纵向整合价值链的成长路径，为单项冠军企业可持续发展提供了有益借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a single-champion enterprise that has long been deeply engaged in the niche field of communication optical fiber and cable, Hengtong has not only formed a leading advantage in professional competition, but also faces the dual challenges of rigid constraints on the capacity and capabilities of the niche market. Through continuous innovation, Hengtong has successfully integrated the entire industrial chain of communication network. In the first stage, the company started with cables and quickly became a leader in the cable field by adopting the &quot;three borrowings&quot; strategy of &quot;borrowing a chicken to lay eggs, borrowing a ladder to climb higher, and borrowing a boat to go out to sea&quot;. In the second stage, to break the reliance on foreign optical fiber raw materials in the upstream of the industrial chain, Hengtong independently developed optical fiber and optical fiber preform technologies, successfully mastering key core technologies and becoming a leader in the global optical fiber communication field. In the third stage, Hengtong, by laying out the downstream market of the industrial chain, launched the fiber-to-the-home solution, and integrated service resources, transformed into a &quot;product + service&quot; general contracting model, and entered emerging fields such as smart cities and marine communications. Its growth path of vertically integrating the value chain provides a useful reference for the sustainable development of single-champion enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理与变革》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全产业链布局（产业链整合理论）；二次创新的演化（二次创新模式）；制造服务化转型（制造服务化模式）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
